Lolita.biografia:
There are several artists named Lolita;

1. Lolita Markovna Milyavskaya (Russian: Лоли́та Ма́рковна Миля́вская, née Горелик (Gorelik); born 14 November 1963) is a Russian singer, actress, TV and film director. She is better known under her stage name Lolita. She was born in Mukachevo, Zakarpattia Oblast, former Ukrainian SSR.

 2. 'Lolita' (María Dolores González Flores) is a Spanish actress and singer who started her career in the early 1970s. <a href="https://www.last.fm/music/Lolita">Read more on Last.fm</a>
